content.html: The best thing about discovering I'm autistic is discovering autistic Twitter and Reddit as a result. Every day now I get to read things that resonate. Things that make me laugh & grin. Before I'd just be so angry and confused at social media. Thanks #actuallyautistic fam! 🙏
